Package: fable
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Title: Forecasting tidy time series
Description: The R package *fable* provides methods and tools for displaying and analysing univariate time series forecasts including exponential smoothing via state space models and automatic ARIMA modelling. Data, model and forecast objects are all stored in a tidy format.
